## Testing standards (verified commands)

**Location:** `backend/tests/` — **`unit/`** (no DB) and **`integration/`** (Postgres + `httpx.AsyncClient`).

**Fixtures (`conftest.py`):** Loads **`.env`** from `backend/` or repo root before importing `app`; provides **`db_session`** (transaction rolled back), **`async_client`** (`get_db` override), **`db_session_with_flush_commit`** / **`async_client_ingest`** (maps `session.commit` → `flush` so `run_ingestion` E2E rolls back cleanly). Integration tests require **Postgres** matching `DATABASE_URL` (e.g. `docker compose up`).

**Pytest / asyncio:** `pyproject.toml` sets **`asyncio_default_fixture_loop_scope = session`** and **`asyncio_default_test_loop_scope = session`** so the async SQLAlchemy engine shares one loop for the session.

**Existing tests (extend these):**

| Area | Files |
|------|--------|
| Validator / parse rules | `tests/unit/test_validator.py` |
| Golden-style totals | `tests/unit/test_golden_aggregate.py` |
| Large-row validate (10k) | `tests/unit/test_large_validate.py` |
| Overlap (mocked session) | `tests/unit/test_overlap_unit.py` |
| Revenue API auth / org scope | `tests/integration/test_revenue_api.py` |
| Ingest unauthenticated + bad extension | `tests/integration/test_ingest_auth.py`, `test_ingestion_e2e.py` |
| Health + auth `/me` + batch 404 | `tests/integration/test_api_smoke.py` |
| Ingest E2E (`run_ingestion` + multipart) | `tests/integration/test_ingestion_e2e.py` |
| Loader unknown BU | `tests/integration/test_loader_dimensions.py` |
| Soft-delete scope | `tests/integration/test_soft_delete_scope.py` |
| Fact uniqueness (DB) | `tests/integration/test_fact_uniqueness.py` |

**Commands (run from `backend/`):**

```bash
cd backend
.venv/bin/pytest tests/ -v
.venv/bin/pytest tests/ --cov=app/services --cov-report=term-missing
```

**Coverage:** Keep **`app/services` ≥ 80%** (`pytest --cov=app/services`); the default suite meets this — re-run after substantive service changes.

**Definition of done for a change touching `app/` or `frontend/src/`:**

1. Relevant **unit or integration** tests added or updated.
2. **`cd backend && pytest tests/ -q`** passes locally (Postgres up for integration tests).

